text: Vasco Joaquim Rocha Vieira, GCTE GCC GCIH ComA (16 August 1939 – 22 January 2025) was a Portuguese Army officer and politician. He was the 138th and last Governor of Macau from 1992 until 1999. Vieira died on 22 January 2025, at the age of 85.Morreu Vasco Rocha Vieira, último governador de Macau ==References== Category:1939 births Category:2025 deaths Category:Portuguese politicians Category:Portuguese military people
